* Maria Laska
* Maria Derwisz-Parnowska
* Zofia Rodziewicz
* Regina Fleszarowa
* and others

==Postwar recognition==
In 1963 ≈ªegota was commemorated in Israel with the planting of a tree in the Avenue of the Righteous at Yad Vashem, with W≈Çadys≈Çaw Bartoszewski present. In 1995 a monument to the organization was unveiled in Warsaw. Another monument was unveiled in 2009 in the Survivors&#x27; Park in ≈Å√≥d≈∫. ≈ªegota is also commemorated in plaques at places of its regional offices in Warsaw and Krak√≥w. In 2009 a commemorative series of coins was issued by the National Bank of Poland.

