** Tiny Kox (10 June 2003 ‚Äì 25 January 2022)
** Rik Janssen (since 25 January 2022)
* Parliamentary leaders in the House of Representatives
** Jan Marijnissen (17 May 1994 ‚Äì 20 June 2008)
