<doc id="356621" wikidata="Q1270737" url="?curid=356621" title="Skaraborg">
<text>[[Skaraborg County]] is a former county of Sweden.

Skaraborg may also refer to:

==Places==
*V√§sterg√∂tland, a historical province of Sweden that includes the area of the former county
*V√§stra G√∂taland County, a current county of Sweden that includes the area of the former county

==Military units==
*Skaraborg Regiment (infantry), former Swedish infantry regiment whose soldiers were recruited from the former county
*Skaraborg Regiment (armoured), Swedish armoured regiment converted from the former infantry regiment
*Skaraborg Brigade, Swedish mechanised brigade that was previously part of the armoured regiment of the same name
*Skaraborg Wing, Swedish Air Force wing</text><links>
